1. This is a flask python application which scrapes the json file and prints out a random line every 10 seconds.
2. Flask application runs on default port i.e. 5001.
3. We will be running app with uwsgi app server, ini file.
4. Nginx will run in either same or different docker as a reverse proxy. Configuration file is present as well.
5. Docker file is present for application.
6. Another dockerfile is to be made for web server.
7. After this we can write a docker-compose file to orchestrate both containers on local.
8. For production we can run the above app in either kubernetes or ECS.
9. We will maintain our infra with terraform and provisioning of servers shall be done with ansible.
